headline: C.H. Robinson gets an upgrade at S&P Global, reduced headcount a key reason
summary: C.H. Robinson had its debt rating increased by S&P Global, and its reduction in staffing is a key reason. The post C.H. Robinson gets an upgrade at S&P Global, reduced headcount a key reason appeared first on FreightWaves.
